Examples for Apache Camel JNB March Article

These examples are built using gradle, which can be installed via http://www.gradle.org . Below are details on how to run each example.

pojo-example
------------
From the pojo-example directory type 'gradle -q run'

seda-example
------------
gradle -q run

jms-separate-jvm-example
------------------------
you'll need to run these from separate consoles as they lock the console and you'll need to ctrl+c to stop them. 
(1) to startup the activemq broker, gradle runActiveMq
(2) to startup the warehouse order listener, gradle -q runWarehouse
(3) finally, to run the example, gradle -q runExample 
The results will appear in the console output for the warehouse


